&lt;h4>클래스&lt;/h4>&lt;p>동작, 공개 메서드, 인스턴스 변수를 나열&lt;/p>
&lt;div class="hextra-code-block hx-relative hx-mt-6 first:hx-mt-0 hx-group/code">
&lt;div>&lt;div class="highlight">&lt;pre tabindex="0" class="chroma">&lt;code class="language-python" data-lang="python">&lt;span class="line">&lt;span class="cl">&lt;span class="k">class&lt;/span> &lt;span class="nc">MyClass&lt;/span>&lt;span class="p">:&lt;/span>
